§451A-5  Powers and duties of the director.  In
addition to any other powers and duties authorized by law, the powers and
duties of the director are to:

     (1)  Adopt rules in accordance with chapter 91 to
carry out the purposes of this chapter;

     (2)  Develop standards for licensure;

     (3)  Prepare and administer examinations;

     (4)  Issue, renew, suspend, and revoke licenses;

